data.description: Welcome to your future home,a beautifully updated 4-bed 4-bath two-story, located in a welcoming neighborhood. This property expresses a modern functional design with many features you are looking for. As you enter, you'll be greeted by an open-concept layout that facilitates a seamless flow between the living spaces. Externally, the home sits on a desirable corner lot providing an ideal backdrop for outdoor activities. The property has undergone significant updates, reflecting a dedication to modern living. The thoughtful layout ensures both convenience and a sense of space, contributing to the overall allure of the residence. Located in a community with favorable tax rates and proximity to excellent schools, this property not only promises a stylish living experience but also underscores the importance of practicality. Embark on the journey to your new lifestyle! Come witness firsthand the charm, convenience & design of this 4-bed, 4-bath, haven.
